---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import TypingAnimation from '../components/TypingAnimation.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="The Hot Dog"
  description="A hot dog is more than a quirky logo. It's a symbol of nostalgia, connection, creativity, and continuity. The origin story of the codewizwit mark."
>
  <article class="hot-dog">
    <!-- Hero + Story -->
    <section class="section-cream section" aria-labelledby="hd-heading">
      <div class="container hd-main-layout">
        <div>
          <p class="label label-gold">The Symbol</p>
          <h1 id="hd-heading" class="hot-dog-title">The Hot Dog</h1>
          <p class="hot-dog-lede">
            A symbol of human connection that's followed me my entire life.
          </p>
          <div class="prose hd-story-prose">
            <p>
              Some of my fondest childhood memories are of sharing Chicago dogs with my
              dad at Gene &amp; Jude's. No ketchup allowed. Small moments that
              taught me how the simplest things can hold the most meaning.
            </p>
            <p>
              Years later, that same symbol showed up again when I hand-carved a
              hot dog block print, "Drag It Through the Garden," for my college capstone project at DePaul. A
              physical artifact made with ink, pressure, and patience.
            </p>
            <p>
              My logo is an AI-generated rendering of my original print.
              A bridge between memory and technology, past and future.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <figure class="hd-side-figure">
          <img
            src="/images/hot-dog-print-sheet.jpg"
            alt="Hot dog block print in blue ink on a restaurant guest check"
            class="hd-side-photo"
            width="422"
            height="764"
            loading="eager"
          />
          <figcaption>The original print on a guest check</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Meta-Proof -->
    <section class="section-dark section" aria-labelledby="hd-proof">
      <div class="container hd-meta-layout">
        <div>
          <h2 id="hd-proof" class="hot-dog-section-heading" style="color: var(--color-cream);">
            The meta-proof
          </h2>
          <div class="prose" style="color: var(--color-gray-light);">
            <p>
              A memory became a carving. A carving became a print. A print
              became a digital logo. The technology changed at every step,
              and the meaning only got stronger.
            </p>
            <p style="color: var(--color-cream);">
              <strong>This is a reminder that while AI can refine creativity and
              carry a symbol forward, the spark, the story, the deeply
              human part always comes first.</strong>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <figure class="hd-meta-figure">
          <img
            src="/images/hot-dog-promo-shoot.jpg"
            alt="Alexandra at Vienna Beef hot dog stand, hands on hips"
            class="hd-meta-photo"
            width="2594"
            height="1722"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <figcaption>"Drag It Through the Garden" Print Installation Promo â€” Chicago, Vienna Beef</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Closing -->
    <section class="section-cream section" aria-labelledby="hd-close">
      <div class="container text-center">
        <h2 id="hd-close" class="hot-dog-closing">
          <TypingAnimation static="More AI." typed=" More human." id="hotdog" />
        </h2>
        <p class="hot-dog-closing-sub">
          The hot dog is a symbol of where I come from, what I care about,
          and the future I want to help build.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .hd-main-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .hd-side-figure {
    position: sticky;
    top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .hd-side-photo {
    width: clamp(220px, 28vw, 340px);
    height: auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .hot-dog-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .hot-dog-lede {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 28rem;
  }

  .hd-story-prose {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .hd-meta-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr clamp(240px, 30vw, 360px);
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .hd-meta-photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .hot-dog figcaption {
    margin-top: var(--space-3xs);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .section-dark figcaption {
    color: var(--color-gray-light);
  }

  .hot-dog-section-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .hot-dog-closing {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .hot-dog-closing-sub {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    max-width: var(--max-width-prose);
    margin-inline: auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hd-main-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .hd-side-figure {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hd-side-photo {
      max-width: 160px;
      margin-inline: auto;
      position: static;
    }

    .hd-meta-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .hd-meta-figure {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hd-meta-photo {
      max-width: 320px;
      margin-inline: auto;
    }

    .hot-dog-lede {
      margin-inline: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
